# Svelte Code Quality

**MANDATORY** when writing or modifying any `.svelte` file or `.ts` file in `src/`:

1. Use the `svelte-autofixer` MCP tool (server: `svelte`) to analyze the code
2. Call it with the complete Svelte component code
3. Iterate until no issues or suggestions are returned
4. Apply all suggested fixes before finalizing

